    "fuel filter": "Diesel fuel filter replacement per BMW fixed-interval schedules for this generation (verify engine code).",
    "gearbox fluid": "Automatic and manual gear oil is often labelled lifetime; many specialists recommend exchange around 100,000 km for long-term health.",
    "coolant flush": "Coolant inhibitor effectiveness declines with age; preventive full exchange around 120,000 km is a common workshop recommendation.",
    "intake carbon clean": "Direct-injection turbo engines can accumulate intake valve deposits; walnut or chemical cleaning around 120,000 km restores airflow."
